    "description": "Alpico Holdings Co., Ltd. engages in the distribution business in Japan. It operates through Distribution Business, Transportation Business, Tourism Business, Real Estate Business, and Other Service Business segments. The company operates food supermarkets under the Delicia brand; commercial product stores under the Gyomu Super Palette brand; mobile sales vehicles under the Tokushimaru name; a self-service unmanned payment store; online supermarkets; pharmaceutical stores; and burger and coffee shops. It is also involved in the bus, taxi, and railway transportation; automobile maintenance, such as vehicle inspection, maintenance, bodywork painting, and vehicle sales; operation of city and business hotels, hot spring resort hotels, inns, and service areas, as well as leisure facilities, including golf courses and campgrounds; travel agency; real estate rental and villa subdivision management business; and insurance activities. Alpico Holdings Co., Ltd. was founded in 1920 and is headquartered in Matsumoto, Japan."
